rows.label: qst100608_msg0001
rows.name:
This too much security to be legal!
Bahn definitely hiding something
inside here!

rows.label: qst100608_msg0002
rows.name:
Maybe we need something like
power of Blade that friends showed
Nilny first time we met.

rows.label: qst100608_msg0101
rows.name:
Amazing!
Friends should apply to SAB!

rows.label: qst100608_msg0102
rows.name:
So contents were...
Bunch of letters?

rows.label: qst100608_msg0103
rows.name:
Correspondence with corrupt
merchants, no doubt!

rows.label: qst100608_msg0104
rows.name:
"To my little Banana,
How are you? Are you eating enough?
Are you being nice to people?"

rows.label: qst100608_msg0105
rows.name:
"Little bird told me you are very
important Nopon now."

rows.label: qst100608_msg0106
rows.name:
"We would like to visit, but Dadapon's
health not up to journey."

rows.label: qst100608_msg0107
rows.name:
"My little Banana must be busy Nopon,
but would be nice to see him sometime.
 Lots of love, Mamapon."

rows.label: qst100608_msg0109
rows.name:
Waaaaahhhh!
This letter filled with love
from Mamapon of Bahn!

rows.label: qst100608_msg0110
rows.name:
This kind of thing always make
Nilny tear up a little...

rows.label: qst100608_msg0111
rows.name:
Even criminal mastermind like Bahn
keep his mamapon's letters like
precious treasure...

rows.label: qst100608_msg0112
rows.name:
Nilny is sorry he think bad of
Bahn... Waahhhhh!

rows.label: qst100608_msg0114
rows.name:
Nilny going to check
all of these letters.

rows.label: qst100608_msg0115
rows.name:
It slightly awkward to check such
private things, but that is job so
Nilny will do it.
